item.title: CVE-2020-1776|2024-09-17T00:26:58.722Z -- otrs%20ag -- %28%28otrs%29%29%20community%20edition
item.description: When an agent user is renamed or set to invalid the session belonging to the user is keept active. The session can not be used to access ticket data in the case the agent is invalid. This issue affects ((OTRS)) Community Edition: 6.0.28 and prior versions. OTRS: 7.0.18 and prior versions, 8.0.4. and prior versions.

item.title: CVE-2020-1770|2024-09-17T01:11:13.158Z -- otrs%20ag -- %28%28otrs%29%29%20community%20edition
item.description: Support bundle generated files could contain sensitive information that might be unwanted to be disclosed. This issue affects: ((OTRS)) Community Edition: 5.0.41 and prior versions, 6.0.26 and prior versions. OTRS: 7.0.15 and prior versions.

item.title: CVE-2020-1766|2024-09-17T00:10:59.231Z -- otrs%20ag -- %28%28otrs%29%29%20community%20edition
item.description: Due to improper handling of uploaded images it is possible in very unlikely and rare conditions to force the agents browser to execute malicious javascript from a special crafted SVG file rendered as inline jpg file. This issue affects: ((OTRS)) Community Edition 5.0.x version 5.0.39 and prior versions; 6.0.x version 6.0.24 and prior versions. OTRS 7.0.x version 7.0.13 and prior versions.
